    "Examples of different hand images of the same number are given in Fig. 8.",
    "Thus, a dataset consisting of a total of 1500 images is obtained.",
    "While creating the dataset, a background consisting of a uniform color (white) is preferred for each hand sign.",
    "It is preferred to have better quality of the input images and to avoid background complexity during training.",
    "In addition, using a uniform background also facilitates the manual labeling process for classification.Prior to commencing the training of the recommended model, a manual classification process was conducted."
